34
00:01:27,527 --> 00:01:30,727
The things that will serve as proof of the alibis are...

35
00:01:30,727 --> 00:01:34,927
foam, steam, and smoke.

36
00:01:34,927 --> 00:01:37,327
Inspector Megure.

37
00:01:37,327 --> 00:01:40,927
Why don't we experiment while we're at it?

38
00:01:40,927 --> 00:01:42,427
Experiment?

